    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="callout callout-blue" style="margin-top:20px">
    <div class="callout-label">Implementation Guidance</div>
    <div class="callout-title">Key Success Factors</div>
    <p style="font-size:13px;color:var(--gray-700);margin-bottom:0">DDSAT assessments are most valuable when conducted with genuine senior executive sponsorship, when SMEs provide honest rather than aspirational responses, and when the resulting findings are connected to binding remediation commitments with named owners and deadlines. The assessment itself has limited value without a disciplined follow-through process. Organisations are encouraged to appoint a dedicated Digital Sovereignty Lead responsible for maintaining the KPI dashboard, coordinating remediation activities, and preparing the annual reassessment — ensuring that DDSAT becomes an embedded governance discipline rather than a one-time exercise.</p>
